T1  - Peer-Confirming Equilibrium
AU  - Lipnowski, Elliot
AU  - Sadler, Evan
Y1  - 2019/03/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA15597
T2  - Econometrica
