T1  - The Interval Structure of Optimal Disclosure
AU  - Guo, Yingni
AU  - Shmaya, Eran
Y1  - 2019/03/01
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/03/01
DO  - https://doi.org/10.3982/ECTA15668
